<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-9527] Cannot create secondary index on a table WITH COMPACT STORAGE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9527</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8156&quot; title=&quot;Fix validation of indexes on composite column components of COMPACT tables&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-8156&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-8156&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; it is said that secondary indexes are not allowed on clustering columns in COMPACT tables.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, I found that it is not possible to create a secondary index on the value column in a COMPACT table:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CREATE TABLE t (&lt;br/&gt;
	a INT,&lt;br/&gt;
	b INT,&lt;br/&gt;
	c INT,&lt;br/&gt;
	PRIMARY KEY (a, b)&lt;br/&gt;
) WITH COMPACT STORAGE;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CREATE INDEX ON t (c);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Bad Request: Secondary indexes are not supported on PRIMARY KEY columns in COMPACT STORAGE tables&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;cassandra v2.0.13&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12834370">CASSANDRA-9527</key>
            <summary>Cannot create secondary index on a table WITH COMPACT STORAGE</summary>
